Titolo: Animal Paradise

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Animal Paradise is a 2007 video game by Agatsuma Entertainment for the Nintendo DS.  It was originally slated for release in North America as Pocket Pets, by O~3 Entertainment. Empire Interactive later published the title as Animal Paradise, as it had already done in Europe. The game features famous photographs from Japanese photographer Yoneo Morita. Its sequel, Animal Paradise Wild, was released in 2009.